verbose_text: Furthermore, it has been previously established that mitogens bind to toll like receptors on B cells, leading to nonspecific B cell activation associated with increased expression of class II associated invariant chain peptide (CLIP) and polyclonal expansion of B cells into immunoglobulin (IgM) secreting (plasma) cells [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: expression of class II-associated invariant chain peptide
